Package: flock
Type: Package
Title: Process synchronization using file locks for UNIX
Version: 0.5
Date: 2014-11-04
Author: Ivan Popivanov
Maintainer: Ivan Popivanov <ivan.popivanov@gmail.com>
Description: Enables synchronization between UNIX processes (spawned by using the "parallel" package for instance) using file locks. An interface to the locking capabilities of "fcntl" system call.
License: Apache License 2.0
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.3)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
